Feelings is a very amazing part of human. I always say I am the type of person who do things based on my feelings. However, is it actually right to do things based on feelings? The feelings to do certain things could be a result of impulsiveness without thinking it through. For me, I can fight the intention to do certain things according to feelings, can you? Perhaps, it is because I do not like to think, that is why I let my feelings make the decision. However, how many of us really willing to think? When we are faced with a problem, most of the time, we just like to avoid and stop thinking and let the feeling work out the decisions. I think this is a very wrong way to settle a problem. Unfortunately, born in this world, there are just too much things to ponder and it is so stressed to think all these things through...